post_text: One of the first New Model Y produced at Giga Berlin, signed by local team Production has now started across all of our 4 vehicle factories around the world – simultaneously Giga Berlin/Shanghai/Texas & Fremont Factory
We are Tesla We’re not just creating products people love – we’re creating a movement for sustainable energy, for everyone
